<HEADLINE>
READY OR NOT, HERE COME 100,000 SOUTHERN BAPTISTS 
</HEADLINE>
   (Commentary)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
 &HT;    
 By DIANA BUTLER BASS  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    As I walked to work this morning, a man stood on a street corner
shouting, ``Do you know Jesus? Repent! Repent or suffer eternal
